snippet.title: Diana Pretend Play with ice cream Cart Toys
snippet.description:
Diana Pretend Play with ice cream Cart Toys. The ice cream carts have a bunch of ice cream toys such as popsicles, ice cream bars, ice cream cones, and a bunch more! Diana and Baby Dolls pretend play buying and selling color ice cream to each other.
